# Styling Standards

## Tailwind

- Use `@theme` in `src/styles/global.css` for semantic colors
- Semantic tokens: `bg-bg`, `text-text`, `text-highlight`, `text-subtle`, `text-faded`, `border-border`
- Dark mode: `@variant dark` via `dark:` utilities

## Spacing

- Use `Spacer` component for vertical/horizontal gaps: `<Spacer axis="vertical" size={8} />`
- Size values: Tailwind spacing scale (e.g. 4, 8, 12, 16, 32)

## Layout

- Use `container` class for page width (defined in global.css)
- `flex flex-row justify-between items-center` for header/footer layouts

## Variant Patterns

- Use `Record<Variant, string>` for style variants:

```astro
const styleVariants: Record<Variant, string> = {
	highlight: 'text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl',
	subtle: 'text-subtle',
}
```
